species_burrbo_desc;The Burrbos, a distant cousin of the Goomba and Galoomba, claim to be the oldest species on the Odyssey Continents, and many theorize them to be a living relic of the oldest form of Goomba, being equated to Shellcreepers. Tending towards vicious temperament, they once held control of the great Thunder Kingdom centuries ago. Nowadays the biggest populations of Burrbos live in stone-age squalor in the Cascade Kingdom. They wouldn't have it any other way.;FRENCH;GERMAN;;SPANISH;;;;;;;;;x
