species_thunder_dragon_desc;Once, long long ago, there was a great empire known as the Thunder Kingdom, whose architecture was built to last a thousand years. Today, that architecture is all that remains of the Thunder Kingdom, brought low in their attempts to harness the power of what they thought was a God. This "God" was the Great Thunder Dragon, who slaughtered the prideful people of the Thunder Kingdom and took its palace as its new nesting ground as repentance. Today, the descendants of that false god rule the Ruined Kingdom with iron claws... May the Moon help them. Long live the Thunder Kingdom.;FRENCH;GERMAN;;SPANISH;;;;;;;;;x
